Sigma Stratum Documentation — Multi-License Notice  
© 2025 Sigma Stratum Research Group

This repository contains documentation, standards, research materials,
and policy texts produced as part of the Sigma Stratum research program.

⚠️ IMPORTANT  
This repository does not use a single uniform license.  
Each document specifies its license explicitly at the top of the file.

Two Creative Commons licenses are used across the corpus:

1. CC BY-NC 4.0 — Attribution–NonCommercial  
   Applied to foundational and non-commercial research documents.

2. CC BY 4.0 — Attribution  
   Applied to commercially-permissive publications.

The specific license applicable to each document is listed:
• at the top of the document itself  
• in the `/legal/` directory (IP Policy, License Overview)

No document may be used under terms different from those listed for that document.

For attribution requirements, permitted uses, and restrictions,
consult the authoritative IP Policy located at:

    /legal/IP Policy

For inquiries regarding licensing and commercial permissions:
eugene@sigmastratum.org
